Algorithm 

Input - Book(Title, Author, Year, ISBM Number, Image)

Process - 
1. prompt the user to add a book 
2. check if the user entered all the required input are entered 
3. save the book 
4. check if the book it is borrowed or not 
5. show the list of books
6. allow users to borrow a book
7. indicate borrowed books
8. give option to return a book after showing the list of books 
9. make returned books available for users 


